---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Salongroei's privacy policy. Learn how we handle your personal data in compliance with GDPR."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <article class="prose-legal">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-expert-navy/50 dark:text-white/50 text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: January 2025
      </p>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Salongroei ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy and processes personal data in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the Dutch GDPR Implementation Act (Uitvoeringswet AVG). This privacy policy explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and how we handle it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Salongroei is an informational website that compares salon software and offers guides for salon owners. We are not a software provider and do not process salon client data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">2. Data Controller</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The data controller for the processing of data via this website is:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-expert-navy/5 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4">
          <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Salongroei</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:info@salongroei.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@salongroei.com</a><br />
            Website: <a href="https://salongroei.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">salongroei.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">3. What Data Do We Collect?</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We collect the following categories of personal data:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Analytics data:</strong> Anonymized usage data via Google Analytics 4 (page views, session duration, device type, geographic region). This data cannot be directly traced to an individual.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Newsletter data:</strong> Email address, if you subscribe to our newsletter.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Contact data:</strong> Name and email address, if you contact us.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Technical data:</strong> IP address (anonymized), browser type and operating system, via server logs.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">4. Purposes of Processing</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We process personal data for the following purposes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
          <li>Improving our website and content (legitimate interest)</li>
          <li>Sending our newsletter (consent)</li>
          <li>Responding to contact requests (performance of a contract)</li>
          <li>Maintaining website statistics (legitimate interest)</li>
          <li>Ensuring the security of our website (legitimate interest)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">5. Legal Basis</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We process personal data based on the following legal grounds under Article 6 GDPR: consent (for newsletter and non-essential cookies), legitimate interest (for website analytics and security), and performance of a contract (for contact requests).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">6. Retention Periods</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We do not retain personal data longer than necessary for the purpose for which it was collected. Analytics data is retained for a maximum of 26 months. Newsletter data is retained until you unsubscribe. Contact data is retained for a maximum of 12 months after the last contact.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">7. Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We only share your personal data with third parties when necessary for our services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Google Analytics:</strong> For website statistics (with IP anonymization enabled)</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Hosting provider:</strong> For technically hosting the website</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Email service:</strong> For sending newsletters</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We never sell your data to third parties. Where possible, we have concluded data processing agreements with our processors.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right of access:</strong> You can request which data we process about you.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to rectification:</strong> You can have incorrect data corrected.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to erasure:</strong> You can request deletion of your data.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to restriction:</strong> You can request restriction of processing.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to data portability:</strong> You can receive your data in a structured format.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to object:</strong> You can object to processing based on legitimate interest.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-expert-navy dark:text-white">Right to withdraw consent:</strong> You can withdraw previously given consent at any time.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          To exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@salongroei.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@salongroei.com</a>. We will respond to your request within 30 days. You also have the right to file a complaint with the Dutch Data Protection Authority (<a href="https://autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl</a>).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">9. Security</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, loss, or destruction. Our website uses HTTPS encryption.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">10. Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The most recent version is always available on this page. For significant changes, we will inform you via our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-black text-expert-navy dark:text-white mb-4">11. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-expert-navy/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Do you have questions about this privacy policy or about the processing of your personal data? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@salongroei.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@salongroei.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
